{'id': 30553014, 'body': "Thank you for the feedback, JKomo. We are currently working to add improvements to the PF App. We appreciate your support as we work to make our app better for you and all our members! 


Please note, you're more than welcome to check-in via your phone number, driver's license, or government issued state I.D.! The PF App is not required to workout in our clubs.
", 'modified': '2022-06-25T19:15:56Z'}

{'id': 25210235, 'body': 'Thank you for the feedback as we are always looking for ways to better optimize the PF App! 

If you have questions or concerns related to a recent visit or experience, please contact your home club directly by going on the PF App and click “Club and Member Support” to submit a request a Contact Us form or call your home gym. 

', 'modified': '2021-09-20T14:26:54Z'}

{'id': 30170908, 'body': 'We are aware of the update concerns plaguing the PF App, 101LP. We're working around the clock to get our app running smoothly for you and all our members. Have you seen a difference since this post?

If possible, you can report this issue by going to "Help!" in the sidebar and tapping "App Technical Support". We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience and any frustration this may have caused!
', 'modified': '2022-06-05T14:50:41Z'}

{'id': 33578447, 'body': 'We hate that you feel this way, Elliot. Unfortunately, per our policy, denim is not allowed to be worn in our clubs while working out! 

f you have questions or concerns related to a recent visit or experience, please contact your home club directly by going on the PF App and click “Club and Member Support” to submit a request a Contact Us form or call your home gym. If you have any technical questions related to the app, we would be happy to help!
', 'modified': '2022-12-07T02:54:53Z'}

{'id': 26153558, 'body': 'Please uninstall and reinstall the PF App. If this doesn't work, on the login page, toward the bottom, there is a yellow "Support" link to click. Please fill out the "App Technical Support" form, add screenshots if you like, and submit.

Also, you can still access our clubs by using your phone number. Please speak to our front desk staff!


', 'modified': '2021-11-08T21:22:42Z'}

{'id': 30170865, 'body': 'We are aware of the update concerns plaguing the PF App. We're working around the clock to get our app running smoothly for you and all our members. Since this post, have you seen any improvement in our app, Matt?

 If possible, you can report this issue by going to "Help!" in the sidebar and tapping "App Technical Support". We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience and any frustration this may have caused!
', 'modified': '2022-06-05T14:44:55Z'}
